	dprr:hasNoteText "Sponsored a law to limit the size of ships which a senator or a senator's son could use in trade (Liv. 21.63.3; cf. Plaut. Merc. 73-78; Cic. Verr. 2.5.45). See Mommsen, Str. 3.899." .
